data.description: This 3 bedroom home has many updates and has already passed the municipal inspection.  Updates include kitchen cabinets and backsplash, kitchen appliances, ceiling fans, lighting fixtures, bathroom fixtures, HVAC, plumbing stack, and water heater.  Wait...  there is a finished lower level with ample space for your entertaining, a utility room for doing laundry, and a large area for storage or???  Finally, you have a great location with easy access to shopping, highway and major thoroughfares.  Did I say "Welcome Home?"
